Title: Alone in Kyoto (Air) but it's in 7/8
Description:
Air
Alone in Kyoto
in 7/8

The video is the scene from Lost in Translation which used the original version of Alone in Kyoto in the same way. It was very lightly re-edited to match the changes to the music.

The remix was made from the released recording--no multitrack, just a stereo file.

I made it on a laptop with bad headphones during the Christmas holidays when I didn't have access to my main computer, but I think it turned out surprisingly well!
